snippet.title: Diana and Roma talk about their favorite holidays
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma will talk about their favorite holidays. 
Let's find out together about your favorite holidays in this educational children's video.
National Hugging Day is an annual event dedicated to hugging. The idea of National Hug Day is to encourage everyone to hug family and friends more often.
Thanks for watching!
